                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Effect</strong> The clockwork dragon breathes a spray of flaming oil that deals [[/r 16d6 #fire]]{16d6 fire damage} in a 40-foot cone (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"37\" data-pf2-traits=\"arcane,evocation,fire,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Breath Weapon DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save).</p>\n<p>Creatures that fail their saves are covered in burning oil and take [[/r 2d6 #persistent fire]] @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Persistent Damage]{Persistent Fire Damage}.</p>\n<p>The clockwork dragon can’t use Breath Weapon again for 2 rounds.</p>"
